												Working in harmony to promote wellbeing and prosperity. With a tradition of service to the community put in place by our Founder, DCM Shriram has been at the forefront ...
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section class="sec-news">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row no-gutters">
				<div class="col-lg col-left">
					<div class="card border-0 rounded-0">
						<img src="/news-img.webp" width="470" height="360" alt="" title="" class="d-none d-lg-block">
						<img src="/news-img-mob.webp" width="682" height="360" alt="" title="" class="d-block d-lg-none img-fluid">
						<div class="card-body card-body-bg card-body-news">
							<h5 class="card-title d-flex">Careers 
